en: I want a rematch, shall we?

pt_BR: Ta afim de perder outra vez ?
en: Are you up for losing again?
Do you want to play soccer with me?

pt_BR: Mas estamos numa quadra de basquete
en: But we’re in a basketball court.
Doesn’t matter, do you want to or not?

pt_BR: Fodase, agora que ja esta aqui na quadra, vai jogar do mesmo jeito!
en: Whatever, now that you’re already on the court, you’re going to play anyway!
